1> looking straight up can help too, while walking backward <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://mywebpages.comcast.net/ssbbrothar/VeraOL2.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=212793">Gander</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=thehawnz>the hawnz</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://images.fotki.com/v13/photos/4/41603/158712/noble-vi.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 123<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/30/02 3:22 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Pinning</span><hr size=1> certain corners in ssrae are nearly impossible to pin.  just practice pulling easy mobs there and seeing how pinning works till you find a corner you like. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=grimmlokk>Grimmlokk</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://grimmlokk.homestead.com/files/icon.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 991<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/30/02 3:59 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://grimmlokk.homestead.com/files/spinhead2.gif?flezbwidth=30&flezbheight=41? WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Pinning</span><hr size=1>  Even if you get the &quot;Can't Hit&quot; message sometimes you're still hitting. If you are shrunk somewhereand getting the message just fiddle with your directions. Face a little left or right. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6122"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://grimmlokk.homestead.com/files/bustedteef2.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=xenojones>XENOJONES</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 502<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/30/02 5:04 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Pinning</span><hr size=1> I look at the floor. Against AOW if you are going to use AT then make sure you are lev'd.<br>
<br>
<br>
